author: arkurth
msg: Updated State.pm::initialize to call update_reservation_lastcheck. This will prevent multiple critical notifications from being sent if an inuse reservation process fails to initialize completely. Rather from attempting to process the reservation over and over again without a delay, vcld will only attempt to process it every 5 minutes.
